</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="998FEBE91ACE87CF74B30F87749A14DD" pageId="null" pageNumber="343" type="description">
<paragraph id="48AC4C12F320BC54551C595D0304FFCD" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
5-40 cm hoch, 
<normalizedToken id="0B78905E5EE967AF6F4896478B32759C" originalValue="büschelig" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">bueschelig</normalizedToken>
. Stengel knickig aufsteigend. 
<normalizedToken id="69363B5144C69A96FADB3ADECD494AB1" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="184336E643A82C8F3B8A3FDE379AE686" originalValue="borstenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">borstenfoermig</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="9906C6957E7022DBAF7FA55BB13F080A" originalValue="Blatthäutchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Blatthaeutchen</normalizedToken>
nicht 
<normalizedToken id="FA57530A2CA6CDD8F2FF83EB82E50C4A" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">ueber</normalizedToken>
1 mm lang, stumpf; 
<emphasis id="AECFD3C2FEBF629D0D67502D99DDAA80" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
oberste Blattscheide den untersten Teil des 
<normalizedToken id="1D9C3CECF9AEE32F92BB7B070ACCA8DC" originalValue="Blütenstandes" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Bluetenstandes</normalizedToken>
meist umfassend. Untere 
<normalizedToken id="84D702266AB77B9D6466A77F4A926588" originalValue="Hüllspelze" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Huellspelze</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="D6757106F9C516CDE2DF451E0D452FD6" originalValue="höchstens" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">hoechstens</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
⅙ 
<emphasis id="74496087ADB0D1E011497C1F1C5E5587" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
so lang wie die obere, oft viel 
<normalizedToken id="12B474C4EB41215F8356FEF6BE65789D" originalValue="kürzer" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">kuerzer</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="9501009514D8EFADECFC82EC7BC83A39" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">nur</emphasis>
1/10 
<emphasis id="697D610975FBB863D2B757CC25A18750" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">so lang</emphasis>
) und eine unscheinbare, 
<normalizedToken id="C6CE88BE934BA8922877D4EF04A0DC62" originalValue="häutige" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">haeutige</normalizedToken>
Schuppe bildend. 
<emphasis id="2F215399CC8B1814A46D181EFF57A56F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
Deckspelzen am Rande und auf dem 
<normalizedToken id="C92225687BC1446B2A55E114589977BE" originalValue="Rücken" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Ruecken</normalizedToken>
lang bewimpert; Haare bis 1 mm lang;
</emphasis>
Granne etwa 
<normalizedToken id="71EA485F61A211CEFAFF2A995FB54356" originalValue="1½" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">11/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie die Spelze; oberste Deckspelze oft ohne 
<normalizedToken id="E63D7A8C3CC9BB6C431C80880DB4C22F" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Bluete</normalizedToken>
und viel kleiner als die untern. - 
<normalizedToken id="04DD1B9FDE71C7FE3B9FF82913EC5B6E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="F6C376B9ECA44C334D401EBE51846940" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="FD71B609C72B80948FE0282AFEC05029" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C2D12879B1A6F4DB8DDB260E1E3E1ED7" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
<emphasis id="4935A3B07A9236F56AA315C3ED627DC2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="057CF71B543598116B0E22081EA88E3D" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
<emphasis id="406E96E379A1D67C653F8B60A1A4F8BC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Offene, trockene, saure, sandige 
<normalizedToken id="97CCDFDC8759D734CD22485A9DCFD262" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="5AAC97EE2441466EE9D095540E80322E" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Aecker</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="8823987CB4DFEA703F5859691F9F465F" originalValue="Wegränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Wegraender</normalizedToken>
, Mauern, 
<normalizedToken id="6A4BE2C0581CB0845FC87C9D03F77AC9" originalValue="Schuttplätze" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Schuttplaetze</normalizedToken>
, Bahnareale.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2322B8335A10FFE5256D09807F41C94C" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
<emphasis id="03ECB36A9E7CAAEBCFA83AC9C7379DA7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
In Westeuropa 
<normalizedToken id="32F548064201EACE9AD063B0B057CE48" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis England; durch das Mediterrangebiet 
<normalizedToken id="F6E88293D6412ED132F6F80654260BE0" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Iran; 
<normalizedToken id="FA225B892A6C2BABD093D74D800CD1D4" originalValue="außerhalb" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">ausserhalb</normalizedToken>
des Areals oft adventiv. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen, 
<normalizedToken id="FBAA72C086EA8470E5626451453451DE" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Ain, 
<normalizedToken id="AEBD92FFA0289A6FFF05E10CF2EE0D68" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">frueher</normalizedToken>
bei Genf, sonst gelegentlich adventiv.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FD0BEF8C49B58DA2EC20FCC89E89CF7B" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">
<emphasis id="7B1FA7DB20333BBB400E80CE1CA98250" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Nach Henrard (1937) ist der Name 
<taxonomicName id="A195BFBDF5D017F408758E23F981EBDA" authority="Tineo" authorityName="Tineo" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Vulpia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="343" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aetnensis">
<emphasis id="490364B0CA480A0DE731ED078E89B4CE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">V. aetnensis</emphasis>
Tineo
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="F9C60B3D7C9E1F40CA7D8551CD803E10" originalValue="gültig" pageId="null" pageNumber="343">gueltig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
